&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/EUR-LONDON-HEDONE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4342&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/EUR-LONDON-HEDONE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- LONDON- HEDONE- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;81&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-14488&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50Best_2015_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;88&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
After garnering rave critical reviews, including &lt;strong&gt;#60 on the World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants 2016&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;list and receiving &lt;strong&gt;one Michelin Star&lt;/strong&gt;, Chef Mikael Jonsson&rsquo;s Hedone, is relatively new on the scene and one not to miss. In a comfortably contemporary dining room with an open kitchen, the finest and unique ingredients-focused tasting menu changes daily. Attire is smart casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact the restaurant by phone at +44-208-747-0377, asking for Aurelie or Tracy, or email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservations@hedonerestaurant.com&quot;&gt;reservations@hedonerestaurant.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, and cell phone or local London (hotel) contact number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant Hedone requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: Restaurant requires&nbsp;24 hours&rsquo; notice of cancellation. A cancellation fee of &pound;25.00 per person will be charged if the reservation is not cancelled within 24 hours of the dining time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation: The restaurant will call you one or two days prior to the dining date to reconfirm and discuss any allergies or special needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

